Class ApplicationActivity

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      org.mobilesynergies.android.epic.service.core.ApplicationActivity
Direct Known Subclasses:
BrowserHistoryProviderActivity, ListEpicActionsActivity
public abstract class ApplicationActivity
extends Activity

Abstract convenience class that handles interaction with the epic service. Activities that are based on the epic service can extend this Activity.
